{"tid":2105960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁卓偉：病人可一傳四 東九沙田高危","createTime":"2020-07-13T04:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T04:48:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a26cb0e98d95efd1403981916c5dfa5c47d9009b","tid":2105960,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200713/SCXXVSIHH5G7WGVJERHATANVZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200713%2FSCXXVSIHH5G7WGVJERHATANVZY%2F&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=83f8a15d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200713%2FSCXXVSIHH5G7WGVJERHATANVZY%2F&h=850ea229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200713/SCXXVSIHH5G7WGVJERHATANVZY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉：病人可一傳四 東九沙田高危<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GgYu0lvLA0SRsy_vZY4wHinMiJs=/700x406/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P52KGU7NKH7D7LVOB5USZQUYPA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGgYu0lvLA0SRsy_vZY4wHinMiJs%3D%2F700x406%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP52KGU7NKH7D7LVOB5USZQUYPA.gif&h=2f2a8215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁卓偉<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港武肺疫情惡化，<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉昨出席電台節目時形容疫情「真係好嚴重」，指港現時才開始真正的持續本地爆發。他指研究報告顯示病毒已出現基因變異，傳染力上升超過三成，平均一名確診者可傳染三至四人。他引述港大研究指，估計本港至少有50至60名隱形患者，而且無法追蹤。梁又指出，現時東九龍及沙田屬較高危「地理群組」，除慈雲山有院舍爆發，周邊地區食肆有確診，其中「的士茶餐廳群組」在坪石一帶，確診的士司機居於新蒲崗、黃大仙、觀塘、油塘至將軍澳等東九龍地區，以流行病學勢趨來說令人憂慮。其中觀塘區是全港人口老化最嚴重的地區，他認為當局應優先為該區居民進行病毒檢測。至於沙田區，他指水泉澳邨的病源很可能來自較早前爆發疫情的瀝源邨，傳播鏈可能一直未停止，只是尚未找到隱形個案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇反駁與基因突變無關<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：袁國勇斥食肆無視限枱令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，袁國勇卻不認同本港<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n天文台前台長林超英則在其facebook發文，分析近日本港確診數字趨勢後預警，當局若無相應措施，本港10日後每日的確診數字或高達數百宗，甚至以幾何級數增長。"},{"pid":"8d4aec557416d572ec5dae52240fa3d3d4b3d5f0","tid":2105960,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:19:29.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，港共同老細都唔CARE，咪有病都繼續返工一齊死囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7e93ef934f8f6512b734db3f18fa2e9ad32940","tid":2105960,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9784c8c78933aa782b1e004c24d6c74c7f0a45d","tid":2105960,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d4aec557416d572ec5dae52240fa3d3d4b3d5f0","tid":2105960,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:19:29.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，港共同老細都唔CARE，咪有病都繼續返工一齊死囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:20:06.000Z","msg":"梁卓偉 自已講過戴口罩講唔到野"},{"pid":"e12855346e2dc8930d9ae0f774797de7dfebc7a1","tid":2105960,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9784c8c78933aa782b1e004c24d6c74c7f0a45d","tid":2105960,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d4aec557416d572ec5dae52240fa3d3d4b3d5f0","tid":2105960,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:19:29.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，港共同老細都唔CARE，咪有病都繼續返工一齊死囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime